'''龍城官邸'''（{{kor|룡성 관저}}）<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.donga.com/Politics/NK/3//20090812/8766418/1|title=‘김정일 저택’ 평양 룡성구역 관저 가능성|work=DongA Ilbo|date=August 12, 2009|accessdate=December 12, 2012|language=ko}}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>又稱'''55號官邸'''（{{kor|55호 관저}}）<ref name="MSNBC">{{cite news|last=Windrem|first=Robert|url=http://dailynightly.msnbc.com/2006/10/in_a_country_of.html|title=Looking down on Kim Jong Il|work=MSNBC|date=June 18, 2010|accessdate=December 12, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20140310143333/http://dailynightly.msnbc.com/2006/10/in_a_country_of.html|archivedate=2014年3月10日}}</ref>或'''主要高級邸宅'''（{{kor|주요 고급 저택}}），是[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國|朝鮮民主主義人民共和國]]最高領導人[[金正恩|金正恩]]的主要官邸。<ref name="Petrov">{{cite web | title= Kim Jong-il’s ‘Mt. Ryongnam Range’ is succeeded by Kim Jong-un’s ‘Mt. Ami Range’ | work= Leonid Petrov’s Korea Vision | url= http://leonidpetrov.wordpress.com/2011/02/16/kim-jong-ils-mt-ryongnam-range-is-succeeded-by-kim-jong-uns-mt-ami-range/| accessdate= December 12, 2012}}</ref>

==位置==
據[[金正日|金正日]]前保鑣[[李英國|李英國]]的敘述，[[平壤市|平壤市]]周圍至少有八座領導人官邸。<ref>{{cite news|title=The Supremo in His Labyrinth|work=Time Magazine|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,201976-1,00.html|accessdate=December 12, 2012 | first=Donald | last=Macintyre | date=February 18, 2002}}</ref>龍城官邸位於[[平壤市|平壤市]]北部的[[龍城區域|龍城區域]]<ref name="Chosun">{{cite news|url=http://english.chosun.com/site/data/html_dir/2009/08/13/2009081300297.html|title='Kim Jong-il's House' Spotted on Google Earth|work=The Chosun Ilbo|date=August 13, 2009|accessdate=December 12, 2012}}</ref>，位於[[金日成廣場|金日成廣場]]東北部約{{convert|12|km|mi|abbr=on}}。整個官邸佔地面積約{{convert|12|km2|mi2|abbr=on}}。<ref name="nkeconwatch">{{cite web | title= Elite Areas | work= North Korean Economy Watch | url= http://www.nkeconwatch.com/nk-uploads/elite1.JPG| accessdate= December 12, 2012}}</ref>

==描述==
該官邸由[[朝鮮人民軍|朝鮮人民軍]]工程旅在[[金日成|金日成]]的指示下修建，於1983年竣工，後由其子[[金正日|金正日]]，以及金正日的妹妹[[金敬姬|金敬姬]]、妹夫[[張成澤|張成澤]]所接管。<ref name="wikimapia">{{cite web | title= DPRK Leadership Compound (Residence 22)| work= Wikimapia | url= http://wikimapia.org/#lat=39.1158035&lon=125.7971087&z=14&l=5&m=b&show=/5407284/DPRK-Leadership-Compound-Residence-22| accessdate= December 12, 2012}}</ref>自金正恩繼承父位以來，將其當作主要官邸。<ref name="Petrov"/>該處配備了地下戰時指揮部，並用覆鉛的鋼筋混凝土牆壁加以掩蓋，以防核戰爭。<ref name="DailyNK">{{cite news|last=Han|first=Young Jin|url=http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02300&num=83|title=Kim Jong Il, Where He Sleeps and Where He Works|work=DailyNK|date=March 15, 2005|accessdate=December 12, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130516044422/http://www.dailynk.com/english/read.php?cataId=nk02300&num=83|archivedate=2013年5月16日}}</ref>外圍裝有電網、雷區及數個安全檢查站。<ref>{{cite news|last=Krauel|first=Torsten|url=http://www.welt.de/print/wams/politik/article11263271/Kim-Jong-ils-Hoehlenstaat-Nordkorea.html|title=Kim Jong-ils Höhlenstaat Nordkorea|work=Die Welt|date=November 28, 2010|accessdate=December 12, 2012|language=de}}</ref>挖有地下隧道，與平壤[[西城區域|西城區域]]長慶洞的[[長慶官邸|26號官邸]]相連通。<ref name="DailyNK"/>內部另有一私用地下火車站。<ref name="RFA">{{cite news|last=Lipes|first=Joshua|url=http://www.rfa.org/english/news/korea/kimspalaces-08172009121508.html|title=Kim's Palaces, via Google Earth|work=Radio Free Asia|date=August 17, 2009|accessdate=December 12, 2012}}</ref>

官邸的裝修也極為奢華。點綴於豪宅<ref>{{cite news|last=Prynne|first=Miranda|url= http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/north-korea-uncovered-palaces-labour-camps-and-mass-graves-1711573.html|title= North Korea uncovered: Palaces, labour camps and mass graves |work=The Independent|date=June 21, 2009|accessdate=December 12, 2012}}</ref>與精心設計的花園<ref name="BBC">{{cite news|last=Brown|first=Adrian|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/8110093.stm|title=Satellites uncover North Korea |work=BBC News|date=August 9, 2009|accessdate=December 12, 2012}}</ref>之間的是數個人工湖，以及各式娛樂設施。據目擊官邸內部的[[脫北者|脫北者]]描述，室內有華美的家居陳設，深廣的長絨地毯和昂貴的枝形吊燈。<ref name="MSNBC"/>

